Text:
I can't get the patch/crack to work.  I've put it in the directory but the programme still says I need to register to get full access.  Can anyone let me know what I need to do?  How do I apply the patch?

Thanks.
Come on guys.  I've been seeding this for a week now and around 100 people have downloaded it since I did.  One of you must be able to help me!
You do the install, then copy the crack file to the install directory, then run the crack. Worked for me... Good luck!
Install, then copy the crack file to the install directory, then run the crack (from the the install directory, of course). Worked for me... Good luck!
